Episodes.Title: Welcome to Vegas
Episodes.Actors: Gordon Ramsay, Jason Santos, Christina Wilson
Episodes.Plot: Gordon Ramsay coaches another selection of hopeful chefs, with the job as head chef at his restaurant in Lake Tahoe and $250,000 going to the winner.

Episodes.Title: Shrimply Spectacular
Episodes.Actors: Gordon Ramsay, Jason Santos, Christina Wilson
Episodes.Plot: Gordon Ramsay tries to mentor aspiring cooks. The contestants are put through their paces as the competition continues to land the $250,000 prize and a job at Hell's Kitchen Lake Tahoe.

Episodes.Title: Hell Caesar!
Episodes.Actors: Gordon Ramsay, Jason Santos, Christina Wilson
Episodes.Plot: The days events involve a Caesar salad challenge. As service begins, the chefs compete to cook for an Olympian and an NFL star at the Chefs Tables, but which team will complete a successful service and who goes home?

Episodes.Title: Wedding Bells in Hell
Episodes.Actors: Gordon Ramsay, Jason Santos, Christina Wilson
Episodes.Plot: Trouble brews in the Red team, with Amber questioning their choice of head chef. The challenge sees the teams tackling a reception for newlyweds, before a difficult service.

Episodes.Title: Hell Starts Taking its Toll
Episodes.Actors: Gordon Ramsay, Jason Santos, Christina Wilson
Episodes.Plot: The teams are tasked with creating Mexican dishes, but only one can enjoy a treat, with the others having to clean out the animal pens. Later, a shock is in store at service.

Episodes.Title: Metal & Marina
Episodes.Actors: Gordon Ramsay, Jason Santos, Christina Wilson
Episodes.Plot: The teams are challenged to put a twist on some classic Italian dishes, with a top reward for the winning group and a morale-sapping punishment for the losers.

Episodes.Title: A Pair of Aces
Episodes.Actors: Gordon Ramsay, Jason Santos, Christina Wilson
Episodes.Plot: The teams take on a compelling surf and turf dome challenge, with the winners enjoying rooftop surfing above the Las Vegas skyline, and the losers making crab-cakes for service.

Episodes.Title: Crapping Out in Hell
Episodes.Actors: Gordon Ramsay, Jason Santos, Christina Wilson
Episodes.Plot: The chefs are met by a craps table. The winning team earns a special lunch, while a miserable fate awaits the losers. There's no dinner service, but someone must leave.

Episodes.Title: Blind Taste Test
Episodes.Actors: Gordon Ramsay, Jason Santos, Christina Wilson
Episodes.Plot: The contestants take part in the blind taste test, with the winners enjoying a helicopter ride, while punishment awaits the losers. Both teams struggle during service - but who will be sent home.

Episodes.Title: There's Something About Marc
Episodes.Actors: Gordon Ramsay, Jason Santos, Christina Wilson
Episodes.Plot: The teams are asked to create five different burgers, with the winners earning a day at Dig This Las Vegas. Dinner service is a struggle for one team, who cannot stop fighting.

Episodes.Title: Sink or Swim
Episodes.Actors: Gordon Ramsay, Jason Santos, Christina Wilson
Episodes.Plot: The chefs compete in the inaugural Spell's Kitchen challenge, with a private pool party the reward. Dinner service caters for important charities, but who will be going home.

Episodes.Title: There's Magic in Hell?
Episodes.Actors: Gordon Ramsay, Jason Santos, Christina Wilson
Episodes.Plot: The Chefs compete in three difficult challenges to prove if they are worthy of a Black Jacket, which all comes down to two chefs fighting for the final one.

Episodes.Title: It's Time!
Episodes.Actors: Gordon Ramsay, Jason Santos, Christina Wilson
Episodes.Plot: The remaining cooks celebrate their success of making it to the final five. Two chefs who have a budding romance, decide to take their celebration to the hot tub.

Episodes.Title: Sleeping With the Enemy
Episodes.Actors: Gordon Ramsay, Jason Santos, Christina Wilson
Episodes.Plot: The final four cook for club goers who have taken over Hell's Kitchen. Dinner service gives each of the chefs a chance to run the pass, but Gordon is out to sabotage them.

Episodes.Title: What Happens in Vegas?
Episodes.Actors: Gordon Ramsay, Jason Santos, Christina Wilson
Episodes.Plot: The chefs are treated to a visit from their families and a tour of Las Vegas. However, their trip to the Jubilee Theatre at Caesar's Palace soon turns into their final challenge.

Episodes.Title: Hitting the Jackpot
Episodes.Actors: Gordon Ramsay, Jason Santos, Christina Wilson
Episodes.Plot: The chefs brief their teams ahead of the most important service of their lives. Following service, the winner and new head chef of Hell's Kitchen Lake Tahoe is announced.
